<br>
It is always a fact that if you kill an innocent man with pre-meditation then you have commited murder. <br>
<br>
This is not the only problem with the death penalty - it *IS* 100% fact that it costs more in every state to kill a man than to keep him locked up.  It is currently the OPINION (no I'm tired of arguing this so here it goes) of most of the world and academic circles that the death penalty does not deter crime.  Those studies based on scientific evidence that have done thier own research have not found any evidence that would show deterrence - and many times the findings would suggest otherwise.<br>
<br>
Is this a problem with the system?  If you like living in the United States it's one you have to accept.  We do try to maintain &quot;Innocent until proven guilty&quot; and &quot;It is better to release 100 guilty men - than imprison 1 innocent&quot;.  Those are the ideals that our leagal system was built on - if you don't like it too bad.  Those statements (in my OPINION) should speak volumes about how the death penalty is applied (ie NEVER).<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> They're both opinions. The second statement is no truer then the first just because society says so.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
That's a very wishy/washy statement.  Muder is a word invented by society - all words are invented and given meaning - all facts/opinions/truth is invented by humans.  We, at one time, believed the world to be flat - it was considered fact.  Society has alot ot say about truth and what is fact.<br>
<br>
There is nothing that is gained by killing someone over putting them in prison for the rest of thier lives, other than vengance perhaps.<br>
<br>
But it still boils down to the fact that I think that the death penalty is murder.  That is because my in my opinion, there is no such thing as leagalised killing.<br>
<br>
I don't grant that the governement - who can't manage to balance a checkbook - has the right to declare a persons termination. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ukerryndarkwater.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kerryn Darkwater</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 1836<br> <font color=#E9D756>(7/22/02 8:48:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3475.topic&index=114>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> It is your opinion that the death penalty is murder. You say so yourself.<br>
